description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-The Beautiful Jungfrau Mountains, Switzerland
-View of Lake Walen in St. Gallen, Switzerland
-Kawaguchiko Lake in autumn
-A cafe-lined street, Sighisoara, Romania
-Cherry trees along Kamo River in Kyoto
-Alpine Lakes Of Slovenia
-Mountain road along Lake Pukaki, New Zealand
-Canal Port of Cesenatico, Italy
-Elba Island, Italy
-Glenveagh National Park, Ireland
name: Pedaling to Panoramas
